FBIS4-58021 "drnes084_d_94001" FBIS-NES-94-084 Daily Report 30 Apr 1994 Libya Al-Qadhdhafi Receives Phone Call From Yemen's al-Bid Al-Qadhdhafi Receives Phone Call From Yemen's al-Bid LD3004185494 Tripoli JANA in Arabic 1815 GMT 30 Apr 94 LD3004185494 Tripoli JANA Arabic BFN [Text] Tripoli, 30 Apr -- Brother 'Ali Salim al-Bid, deputy chairman of the Presidential Council in Yemen, made a phone call to the brother leader of the revolution [al-Qadhdhafi] during which he expressed his concern over the deteriorating situation in unified Yemen. Brother 'Ali Salim al-Bid stressed that the Arab nation must intervene to save Yemen from a civil war and fratricide.
